 your first home? Download the free app today</h2><p>Halifax won't just help you buy a home – it will help you find one, too. The free Halifax Home Finder App, available on iPhone and Android smartphones, lets you:<br />&#149; Search for properties on the move<br />&#149; Take and share notes<br />&#149; Find out how much you could borrow<br />&#149; Get helpful tips about the home buying process</p><p>Visit your app store, or go to <a href=\"http://mobile.halifax.co.uk/finder\"rel=\"nofollow\">mobile.halifax.co.uk/finder</a> to download the Halifax Home Finder App for free today.</p><figure data-media-id='gu-image-420747757'><img src='http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/commercial/2013/10/11/1381504162245/repossessed.jpg' alt='YOUR HOME MAY BE REPOSSESSED IF YOU DO NOT KEEP UP REPAYMENTS ON YOUR MORTGAGE' width='460' height='75' class='gu-image'/><figcaption></figcaption></figure><p>Halifax is a division of Bank of Scotland plc, Registered in Scotland No. SC327000. Registered Office: The Mound, Edinburgh EH1 1YZ. Bank of Scotland plc is authorised by the Prudential Regulation Authority and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority and the Prudential Regulation Authority. Information correct at 23rd October 2013. Compliance No. 13/06877</p><!-- Guardian Watermark: internal-code/content/419726705|2013-11-11T15:34:05Z|9853547bd42c534f3ba34683689d5b645aaefd46 -->",
